item.title: Walter White has been on Better Call Saul the whole time - and sheâ€™s breaking bad
item.description: This post assumes the reader has an up-to-date knowledge of the events of Better Call Saul through the first two episodes of Season 6. Imagine reaching a point in your relationship with your partner where you feel comfortable telling them about something private you enjoy that is intensely personal, unusual, possibly dark, and likely off-putting to most people. You figure the worst thing that can happen is that they dislike it so much you both never talk about it again.
